Description: build and customize Ubuntu/Debian live ISO images
 DistroForge is a Python toolkit for planning, validating and building
 customized Ubuntu/Debian live ISO images.
 .
 It provides a classic CLI, optional Typer facade, Qt GUI launcher, dry-run
 planning, ISO build orchestration, branding, QA helpers, provenance output,
 plugin hooks and beginner-oriented guardrails.
